{"tid":2211663,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"解放軍導彈標靶疑脫落　隨水漂流市民拖上岸","createTime":"2020-09-21T09:20:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-22T09:43:36.000Z","uid":271829,"like":21,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"45316e49e4d0d89e8026e656a9c3395364df9080","tid":2211663,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T09:20:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20200921/photo/bkn-20200921090204048-0921_00952_001_01p.jpg?20200921094039\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20200921%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200921090204048-0921_00952_001_01p.jpg%3F20200921094039&h=67a0903d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n解放軍導彈標靶疑脫落隨水漂流，被市民拖上岸。<br />\n<br />\n解放軍近月多次在渤海、黃海、東海、南海等進行實彈射擊演練，有內地網民近日在海邊發現一個寫有「導彈標靶，立即遠離」的標靶，疑是脫落後隨水漂流。<br />\n網傳片段顯示，一個大型橙色物體在海上漂流，然後被沖上岸邊，2名少年拉起物體旁邊的繩子，合力將它拖上岸。有網民稱「撈上來都没有用了」，又笑稱不要將標靶拿回家，「小心中彈」。"},{"pid":"17bf0c62cff7dcb1cc655a4a36eca12159dd6851","tid":2211663,"uid":28743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T09:23:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d471fd50cf77d4ef847098701bcf3f2e907018e9","tid":2211663,"uid":122134,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T09:23:30.000Z","msg":"即係粒野就算漂左上岸<br />\n都一野炸落去?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1cb4d4b9ce401cdbb8bb05c6b39f113f561c290","tid":2211663,"uid":54125,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T09:24:37.000Z","msg":"即係導彈無打中個靶？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39dfe9bd88188281dfaf611ebc37469d6d5e336b","tid":2211663,"uid":103325,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T09:27:19.000Z","msg":"寫到明立即遠離都仲要拖上岸想拎返屋企&hellip;有無咁撚貪心呀"},{"pid":"8ce4f67979fa211df18d8